{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You needed an affidavit in order to immigrate to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You needed a quota number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You needed-- you needed to know someone who would give you an affidavit, which meant putting away a certain amount of money, I think, for one or two years.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As far as I remember, that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we always said that we will not be-- we all have professions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we told them we can sew, and we can do all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- and we begged, and we even enclosed a reply-- a reply stamp, something like that, so it wouldn't cost them any money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had a few responses but no affidavits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we were really-- and this went on into '37.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But in '37, the situation of getting into a-- you could get out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it seems that one country after the other closed their doors, because meanwhile, the Jewish-- many of the Jewish people had gone to other countries.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- and I guess many of the countries realized that they're getting a lot of Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember it was very hard to go any place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember my mother saying, I-- I'll go to the jungle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If I could just go anyplace and just live on bread and water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it was-- we just couldn't go any place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had no place to go to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Especially in 1937, it was-- we-- we tried very hard to-- to go away to any place, whoever would want to take us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We could not get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We could get out, but we couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any changes in the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, in the laws about-- for Jews?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were always changes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always something new coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
